=== written_bytes is bucketed per normalized query hash for async inserts ===
--- pattern A (Values), first insert is within the per-pattern limit ---
allowed
--- pattern A, second insert is still within its own bucket ---
allowed
--- pattern A, third insert exceeds its own bucket ---
QUOTA_EXCEEDED
--- pattern B (JSONEachRow, a different format hence a different hash) has its own bucket ---
allowed
--- pattern B, second insert is still within its own bucket ---
allowed
--- pattern B, third insert exceeds its own bucket ---
QUOTA_EXCEEDED
